tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE reports (
    report_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    report_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    revenue DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    profit_margin DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    customer_satisfaction INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE profit_margin_report (
    report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    report_date DATE,
    total_cost DECIMAL,
    total_revenue DECIMAL,
    profit_margin DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE RevenueReports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    revenue_amount DECIMAL,
    report_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE ProfitMargins (
    margin_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    margin_value DECIMAL,
    margin_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerSatisfaction (
    satisfaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    satisfaction_score INT,
    feedback_text TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE RevenueAndProfit (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    revenue_amount DECIMAL,
    profit_amount DECIMAL,
    report_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    feedback_date DATE
)
